OL,3,CCouncil drops attempts to block RAF
OL,4,Cbase asylum seeker plan
OL,6,FA council has dropped its attempts to
OL,7,Fblock the conversion of a former RAF
OL,8,Fbase into a reception centre for
OL,9,Fasylum seekers.
OL,11,FWest Lindsey District Council
OL,12,Fannounced it had withdrawn an
OL,13,FenforcementJnotice at RAF Scampton
OL,14,Fafter the Home Office confirmed it had
OL,15,Flaid a Special Development Order (SDO)
OL,16,Fin Parliament.
