OL,4,Cbase asylum seeker plan
OL,6,FThe order grants temporary planning
OL,7,Fpermission for the site to be used for
OL,8,Fasylum accommodation, meaning the
OL,9,Fcouncil has no grounds to pursue
OL,10,Fenforcement action.
OL,12,FCouncil leader Trevor Young said: "The
OL,13,Fcouncil has been clear from the outset
OL,14,Fthat theJuse of an SDO excludes the
OL,15,Fvoice of our communities from being
OL,16,Fheard.
