OL,3,CCouncil drops attempts to block RAF
OL,4,Cbase asylum seeker plan
OL,6,F"We know this is incredibly important
OL,7,Ffor our communities and we are
OL,8,Fcommitted to continuing to do all we
OL,9,Fcan to represent their views and to
OL,10,Fprotect the #300million investment
OL,11,Fplan, which we still believe is the
OL,12,Fright way forward."
OL,14,FSally Grindrod-Smith, director of
OL,15,Fplanning, said: "It is no longer
OL,16,Fexpedient for the Council to continue
OL,17,Fwith its current enforcement action.
