OL,4,Cbase asylum seeker plan
OL,6,F"There are a significant number of
OL,7,Fconditions associated with the SDO,
OL,8,Fwhich the Home Office has to attend to
OL,9,Fbefore the site can go live.
OL,11,F"We as a council will be monitoring
OL,12,Fclosely these conditions and seeking
OL,13,Fassurance from the Government of its
OL,14,Fcompliance."
OL,16,FThe Home Office had already confirmed
OL,17,Fit was reducing the number of people
OL,18,Fto be on site from 2,000 to 800 with a
OL,19,Fcaveat to increase the number of
OL,20,Fpeople by 300, if there is a higher-
OL,21,Fthan-expected demand for spaces.
